The paper discusses the societal impacts of big data, which involves various aspects of computer science such as data management (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on legal and ethical issues related to big data, which falls under the category of computational society (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the potential benefits of big data in various domains, which could be classified under social and information sciences (cs.SI).
